lead_paragraph: Antoine Griezmann struck two goals, one in the 93rd minute, to give Atletico Madrid a 2-1 Group D win over Rostov on Tuesday that took them into the Champions League last 16 and preserved their 100 percent record.

headline.print_headline: Griezmann's Late Goal Takes Atletico Through to Last 16
